cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with anomaly detection in surveillance videos using a Siamese convolutional neural network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, specifically deep learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves multimedia processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, since the paper deals with surveillance videos, it could also belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
